summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5888 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 3, Sea View Park Addition, being the alley between 41st Avenue Southwest and 42nd Avenue Southwest, from West Brandon Street to West Dawson Street; and certain other alleys; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 77588, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
